{"tid":643163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先食m記，有個大陸女人","createTime":"2018-04-26T10:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T12:48:52.000Z","uid":42407,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c3531c63b63fa5f509cce3174699bd92f3936d94","tid":643163,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"拎盒雞翼分享盒去話人地比少咗兩舊雞<br />\n之後去搵經理黑面，當經理同佢加緊，點知佢個細仔話家姐食緊，個大陸女人柒下柒下同個女講我以為你食緊個包，到個經理係廚房出翻黎比佢，個女人隻字不提成盒拎走，個經理又唔知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個大陸女人咁就多咗兩舊雞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實香港點解會拎到咁？淨係講句sorry搞錯咗都唔識？你班蝗成翻上去啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/180707_58a58826ee372ca0ee18bde634e57712.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F180707_58a58826ee372ca0ee18bde634e57712.png&h=9909f31c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57cfa40068450dec6db574f2012fd95464967414","tid":643163,"uid":42407,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"身教都唔撚識<br />\n仔女點會認錯"},{"pid":"6321384fd9d92fbf8b6ea99b96d435a353abd64c","tid":643163,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d7b74e95cec05da097be09b5ad1ab24368834cd","tid":643163,"uid":181824,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:14:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b888b86daace53f178284c2b852a4c3b3615bf41","tid":643163,"uid":42407,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"6321384fd9d92fbf8b6ea99b96d435a353abd64c","tid":643163,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"又無咗#3"},{"pid":"22c7f72f99482320442daae7d6db9d4a5ad57cf7","tid":643163,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0